---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const title = 'Privacy Policy — FunMath Tools';
const description = 'Privacy policy for FunMath Tools. Learn how we handle your data, cookies, and protect your privacy.';
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-8">
    <nav class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-6">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-brand-500">Home</a>
      <span class="mx-2">/</span>
      <span>Privacy Policy</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-500 mb-8">Last updated: April 2026</p>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-8 prose prose-slate max-w-none">
      <p class="text-slate-700">
        At FunMath Tools, we take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our website.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 mb-3">
        FunMath Tools is designed to work without requiring personal information. We do not require sign-ups, accounts, or email addresses to use our tools and games.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-700 mb-3">However, we may collect:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
        <li><strong>Local Storage Data:</strong> We use browser local storage to save your game scores, preferences, and progress on your own device. This data never leaves your device.</li>
        <li><strong>Anonymous Usage Statistics:</strong> We may collect anonymous data about how the site is used (page views, popular tools) to improve our services.</li>
        <li><strong>Technical Information:</strong> Standard server logs (IP address, browser type, device type) for security and performance.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">2. Cookies and Similar Technologies</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 mb-3">
        We use cookies and similar technologies to:
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
        <li>Remember your language preference</li>
        <li>Save your game scores and settings</li>
        <li>Analyze website performance (anonymously)</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-slate-700 mt-3">
        You can disable cookies in your browser settings, but some features may not work properly.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">3. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 mb-3">
        We may use third-party services that have their own privacy policies:
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
        <li><strong>Google AdSense:</strong> We may display ads to support our free service. Google may use cookies to show personalized ads. Learn more at <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" class="text-brand-500 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Ad Policy</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> We may use Google Analytics to understand site usage anonymously.</li>
        <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> Our hosting provider may collect security and performance data.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">4. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700">
        FunMath Tools is designed to be safe for users of all ages. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent and believe your child has provided personal information, please contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@funmath.tools" class="text-brand-500 hover:underline">contact@funmath.tools</a>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">5. Data Security</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700">
        We use industry-standard security measures to protect any data we handle. Since we don't collect personal information by default, your privacy risk is minimal.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">6. Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700 mb-3">You have the right to:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
        <li>Clear your local storage data anytime via your browser settings</li>
        <li>Block cookies in your browser</li>
        <li>Use ad-blocking software</li>
        <li>Contact us with privacy concerns</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700">
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">8. Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-700">
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-700 mt-2">
        📧 <a href="mailto:contact@funmath.tools" class="text-brand-500 hover:underline">contact@funmath.tools</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
